{"tid":664932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國品牌GAP「中國地圖T恤」沒台灣、藏南和阿克賽欽等地區  中國網友玻璃心又崩潰","createTime":"2018-05-14T13:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T00:06:06.000Z","uid":35790,"like":328,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"0cbd74ffccb850698097cb517029e53ba31ac0bb","tid":664932,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"GAP「中國地圖T恤」沒台灣 中國網友玻璃心又崩潰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpaTh5R4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpaTh5R4.jpg&h=6ae2e293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日前有中國網友在微博貼出一款美國品牌GAP所出的T恤，衣服上印製的中國地圖，被網友指控是「刪減後的中國地圖」，因為台灣、藏南和阿克賽欽等地區皆未繪入，且渤海一帶形狀也變形。此照片在微博上瘋傳，不少網友崩潰表示「中國一點都不能少」。事後，GAP回應「目前此款服裝並未在中國發售」，引發中國網友一陣撻伐，並揚言要「封殺此公司」。<br />\n<br />\n據中國媒體《環球網》報導，今（14）日有網友在微博上傳一張GAP的T恤照，此款T恤上繪製了一塊紅色的中國地圖，地圖上卻未包含台灣、藏南和阿克賽欽等地區。許多網友紛紛轉發此照片，並憤怒表示要「封殺此公司！」、「不注重中國人民的感受以後就不買他家東西！」<br />\n<br />\n據報導，《環球網》為此致電詢問GAP中國總部，得到「目前此款服裝並未在中國發售」的回覆，更讓網友怒批「在中國未發售此款，在其他地區發售了？那麼就是有意為之！」報導中還張貼了「中國一點都不能少」的圖片以示抗議。<br />\n<br />\n去年奧迪汽車也曾使用過這種「少了幾點」的中國地圖，燃起了中國網友的憤怒，奧迪在事發隔日便為「此舉傷害了中國人民的感情」而發出道歉聲明。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2425752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2425752&d=oSQATcPEiOS3RqyQsNV7tTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8d67cba9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2425752&h=03668083\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2425752</a>"},{"pid":"96eb3ac47c9c4214cadf99192f76e07eaa6987c5","tid":664932,"uid":35790,"like":289,"dislike":0,"score":289,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"聽日去買番件"},{"pid":"d9ff296e6977cfe3fbbded1bb2c25df9909d8180","tid":664932,"uid":31962,"like":248,"dislike":1,"score":247,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"封殺此公司但想要綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834106a39d857fa8768b127f303475132b34d5b4","tid":664932,"uid":21716,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:35:31.000Z","msg":"海參威呢"},{"pid":"3c603c86c899f4281675ddbf557123899678345e","tid":664932,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354c8450bdab9e8d3eacc9aef446859ec7d06e62","tid":664932,"uid":135767,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ddad8678715b1c23e38a0f450ee66d6c58c4c80","tid":664932,"uid":35790,"like":119,"dislike":0,"score":119,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"Gap<br />\nV city<br />\n屯門<br />\n<br />\n中環<br />\n<br />\nNew Town Plaza Phase 1<br />\n沙田<br />\n<br />\n海港城<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀"},{"pid":"d94826447b4463de9dcaef74be762370486a9ea5","tid":664932,"uid":47674,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"quote":{"pid":"96eb3ac47c9c4214cadf99192f76e07eaa6987c5","tid":664932,"uid":35790,"like":289,"dislike":0,"score":289,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:32:47.000Z","msg":"聽日去買番件"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"童裝嚟架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來同系列有另外幾個國家<br />\n但全部都用國旗<br />\n只有支那唔用五星旗（應該係法律所限）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/214950_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F214950_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=104ec7b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a23394305d74b5259603e47032ec53d21473c549","tid":664932,"uid":173397,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56942ac71f947a84e68404d08e230600a32daa83","tid":664932,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi